  description="Repairs, remodels, structural work, and commercial upkeep across the Bay Area with dust control, coordinated trades, and one accountable site lead."
>
  <section class="relative overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-br from-neutral-white via-neutral-light to-white section-padding">
