            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary"></span>Waterproofing and drainage</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary"></span>Roofing, siding, and trim</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="bg-secondary text-neutral-light section-padding">
      <div class="section-container space-y-10">
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-center md:justify-between gap-6">
          <div class="space-y-3">
            <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-accent">How we work</p>
            <h3 class="display-font text-3xl md:text-4xl font-semibold text-neutral-white leading-tight">Steady rhythm, tidy sites.</h3>
            <p class="text-neutral-light-gray text-lg max-w-2xl">
