            <p class="display-font text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-white mb-1">Scope & site walk</p>
            <p class="text-neutral-light-gray text-sm leading-relaxed">Document conditions, risks, and quick wins; align budget targets and constraints.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-2xl bg-neutral-white/5 border border-white/10 p-5">
