        <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-primary">Why it works</p>
        <h4 class="display-font text-3xl md:text-4xl font-semibold text-secondary leading-tight">One lead, tidy protection, predictable schedules.</h4>
